msgctxt "QL_GoronMini_WallCrackTBox_Desc"
msgid ""
"Dugby, the young Goron soaking in the\n"
"Goron Hot Springs, said: \n"
"\n"
"\"I bid a <1.se_co>tweshure<2.re_co> binteen gear an ba\n"
"<3.se_co>Bridge of Eldin<4.re_co>! Iz an abazing "
"<5.se_co>schtick<6.re_co>!\n"
"Beely bool! If boo bind it...iz boars!\"\n"
"  \n"
"It sounds like gibberish, but maybe there's\n"
"something to it after all?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_GoronMini_WallCrackTBox_Finish"
msgid ""
"The treasure that young Goron Dugby hid and\n"
"alluded to turned out to be...a drillshaft!\n"
"\n"
"Since you found it, he's going to let you\n"
"keep it."
msgstr ""

